# Optional: when embedded PostgreSQL is flaky on your machine, point Paperclip at your
# container, Railway Postgres, or team Postgres. Copy these lines to:
#   %USERPROFILE%\.paperclip\instances\default\.env
# (Create the `instances\default` folders if they do not exist.)
# Railway: railway login && railway link, then see doc/DATABASE.md section "Railway".
#
# DATABASE_URL=postgres://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:5432/postgres
